WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:05.600
Since Hank, numerous commercial packaged
telehomecare systems, including

00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:10.800
one I was involved in developing
in the late 1990s, have sought to

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:15.420
assist patients in recording subjective
data about aspects of their care.

00:00:15.420 --> 00:00:18.690
Including their symptoms,
their activity level.

00:00:18.690 --> 00:00:22.870
And very importantly their compliance
with their treatment plan as well of

00:00:22.870 --> 00:00:27.630
course as objective data typically
obtained by devices about their weight,

00:00:27.630 --> 00:00:31.160
blood pressure, pulse, temperature,
and even their electrocardiogram.

